## base.AnyMatcherWithExample class

The base class for all Test Equivalence Matchers that have examples provided. Extend this if your matcher knows what the example will be. Otherwise, use [base.AnyMatcher](./test-equivalence-matchers.base.anymatcher.md)

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare abstract class AnyMatcherWithExample extends AnyMatcher
```
